*&quot;Revenge&quot; (demos with Pete Pavli – recorded 1980s, released 1999)
*&quot;Centigrade 232&quot; (Voiceprint, 2007). Spoken word. Released as book/CD (VP403CDMO) and CD (VP403CD 2007)

===Live albums===
