* &quot;Life as We Know It&quot; (1987)
* &quot;The Earth, a Small Man, His Dog and a Chicken&quot; (1990)
* &quot;Building the Bridge&quot; (1996)
* &quot;Find Your Own Way Home&quot; (2007)
* &quot;Not So Silent Night ... Christmas with REO Speedwagon&quot; (2009)

