* Akihabara, Tokyo, Japan
* Apliu Street, New Kowloon, Hong Kong
* Business cluster
* Electronic waste
* In London, until the early 1980s there were shops selling surplus electronics on Tottenham Court Road, Edgware Road, and Lisle Street.
* Yongsan Electronics Market, Seoul, Korea
* Guang Hua Digital Plaza, Taipei, Taiwan
* Pudu Market, Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia
* Tin Pan Alley
* York Street, Sydney, Australia

